{"tid":178378,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Gantz上唔上得神台","createTime":"2017-03-29T13:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T16:14:24.000Z","uid":57364,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22321dfed2f99ff67fac73508a4859b8113819b4","tid":178378,"uid":57364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/gantz/images/5/54/Cast.png/revision/latest?cb=20130922214754\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fgantz%2Fimages%2F5%2F54%2FCast.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130922214754&h=9645d6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫風方面初初睇好怪，但慣左之後覺得勁正，由其佢背景係直情用真相去整(好似係)，好真實FEEL。<br />\n<br />\n劇情方面有時可以當H漫睇(羅拉超好J)，又有血腥，又破格(主角群可以隨時死，估唔到)，而且篇篇總有高潮位，又有連貫性，又有好多特殊劇情同設定，夠天馬行空又過癮，唔會一味玩王道(複製玄野，無啦啦有第三方吸血鬼亂入，殺多惠)<br />\n<br />\n氣氛營造NO.1，間唔中會打超勁BOSS,好有絕望感(佛像，用雷個隻野，大版篇)，而且為左最終篇前舖左個意大利篇，果陣真係睇到呆哂，俾D鵰像HIGH一野即刻收皮，連GANTZ都壞Q埋，然後就到世界末日真係一野直上高潮。<br />\n<br />\n人設上基本每個人都好鮮明，好好J嘅羅拉同麗佳，好Q煩嘅玄野同多惠，好西嘅西，大隻佬配正太，仲有好正氣嘅加藤。<br />\n<br />\n最終篇D寓意係BONUS，外星人對我地其實同我地對D動物一樣，放血，剌身，釣蝦咁釣，當寵物養死，一腳踢死。<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解依套野係香港咁冷門，齊齊推GANTZ上神台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1253dc29a57bee03cb86374c10393fb68b025ec","tid":178378,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"講返條吸血鬼線先再講"},{"pid":"7e6fd25a36636e575bb5b5d2f0c10847fcc3ab80","tid":178378,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"gantz都冷門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361460929c226bf1dedb2f155890447501f4338f","tid":178378,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=